\id EPH - Mbula
\h Amǝ Afisu
\toc3 Afi
\toc2 Amǝ Afisu
\toc1 Amǝ Afisu
\mt2 Cauterǝa mala Bulǝs aban ká a ban
\mt1 AMƏ AFISU
\imt1 Mǝncau
\im \bk Cauterǝa mala Bulǝs aban ká a ban amǝ Afisu \bk* ka, Bulǝs nǝ̀ gilǝì a bàkú mana nda a ndàkurban a Roma ka. Cau mǝgule aɓa mǝnia yì cauterǝa ka nda mana ama Ɓakuli kanina nǝ̀ dapi koya gir mǝnana a kùli andǝ nzali kat aɓata rǝcandǝa mala Kǝrǝsti. Yì cauterǝa ka ɓakɓabum amǝkwaɗi ɓǝa dukdo a njar mana nǝ̀ lǝmdǝa aɓa mǝsǝcau ama à dumǝna mwashat, bangŋe na a mburkun nǝmurǝì ɗang.
\ip Mǝgilǝgir bang cau amur: njargula mǝnana Ɓakuli Tárrú kǝ tarkina aɓwana male nǝi, kǝ twalia wia banì, sǝ kǝ panzǝia aɓalǝ acauɓikea malea nǝ bu Yesu Kǝrǝsti, yì Muni, andǝ pa mǝnana pa Bangŋo Mǝfele ace lǝmdǝ ama pacau male mǝgule mǝnana pa ka, mǝsǝcau na nǝ̀ lumsǝì.
\ip Mǝgilǝgir pak túró nǝ akanicau ɗàngɗáng ace lǝmdǝ dotarǝu mǝ'mwashati mala aɓwana mala Ɓakuli aɓa kpapi malea andǝa Kǝrǝsti. Ikǝlisiya ka nda kǝla nggūrǝu, mǝnana Kǝrǝsti do nda ɓamuru; sǝ a ɓè njarì ka, nda kǝla ɓǎh, mǝnana Kǝrǝsti do nda nggea tali mǝgule mǝnana bwal kusǝ ɓǎh ka; sǝ a ɓè njar ɗǝm ngga Ikǝlisiya do kǝla ɓwama, mǝnana Kǝrǝsti do kǝla bura ɓwama ka.
\iot Agir mǝnana a ɓālǝi ka
\io1 Mǝn cau\ior 1:1-2\ior*
\io1 Kǝrǝsti andǝ Ikǝlisiya\ior 1:3--3:21\ior*
\io1 Bǝsa yilǝmu aɓa Kǝrǝsti\ior 4:1--6:20\ior*
\io1 Masǝlǝata cau\ior 6:21-24\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Makkun mala Bulǝs
\p 
\v 1 Mǝnia yì cauterǝa ka pur nǝ bu Bulǝs, mǝnana à tàrì, à twali nǝ eare mala Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ duk mǝ'mishan mala Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka.
\p Gilǝ mǝnia yì cau ka aban ká a ban aɓwana mala Ɓakuli, yì amǝkwaɗi mǝnana à pa ɓamuria aban Kǝrǝsti Yesu nǝ mǝsǝcau, a nggea-là Afisu ka.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 18:19-21; 19:1\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 2 Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli Tár sǝm andǝ Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu Kǝrǝsti lǝmdǝa wun ɓwamuru sǝ ɓǝ̀ pa wun dorǝpwala.
\s1 Ɓakuli tsǝ́ngŋǝ̀nà sǝm bu // kǝ̀rkǝ́r aɓa Kǝrǝsti
\p 
\v 3 Ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɓwangsǝ Ɓakuli, Tár Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti, mǝnana tsǝ̀ngŋǝ́nà sǝm bu nǝ́ koya tsǝkbu mala Bangŋo, mana kǝ yiu nǝ́ kuli ka, aɓa kpapi ma'sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti.
\v 4 Kaniama nǝ̀ pak ɓanza ka, Ɓakuli ak tadǝmba tàr sǝm, ɓǝ̀ sǝm duk amale, aɓa kpapi ma'sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm tàr ɓamur sǝm aceì, ɓǝ̀ sǝm duk aɓwana amǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ a baní, sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm dukdo earcearǝu.
\v 5 Ɓakuli ak dǝmba ɗiɗyal kànì a bumi ama, nǝ̀ pa sǝm bancame mala duk amuni nǝ bu Yesu Kǝrǝsti. Mǝnia ka nda earkiyi ce, sǝ ban kǝ ɓoari wi arǝì ka.
\v 6 Ace mani ka, sǝm nggǝ ɓwangsǝ Ɓakuli ace ɓwamuru male mǝgule mǝnana soapa sǝm mi amur sǝm, sǝm aɓwana mǝnana sǝm nda ka mala Muni mǝnana earkiyi ace raka.
\v 7 Yì ka, mǝsǝswatǝr andǝ ɓwamuru male ka à gul kǝ̀rkǝ́r, nda sǝ yi kúr panzǝban ma'sǝm nǝ nkila mala Muni, pǝlǝa twala sǝm ban acauɓikea ma'sǝm ngga.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 1:14\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 8 Yi soapa sǝm pe mǝɓoarne male nyangsang amur sǝm, andǝ sǝlǝe andǝ súrǝè kat.
\v 9 Adyan ngga, Ɓakuli lǝmdǝna sǝm kane male mǝnana lǝmdǝí aban kǝɓwa ɗiɗyal raka, mǝnana kani ace lùmsǝ banɓoarnado male nǝ bu Kǝrǝsti ka.
\v 10 Sǝ mǝnia ka nda kànì male: Ɓǝ̀ pwarì yi kārǝ́na ka, Ɓakuli nǝ̀ dapi koya gìr mǝnana a kùli andǝa mǝnana a nzali kat ka aɓata rǝcandǝa mala Kǝrǝsti.
\p 
\v 11 Sǝ acemǝnana à dapina sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti ka, sǝm kumǝna liɓala a bu Ɓakuli, acemǝnana ak dǝmba tàr sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm duk amale aɓa kpata kane male, sǝ yì nǝ nggearǝì ka kǝ tsǝk koya gìr ka ɓǝ̀ pa kǝla mǝnana ɓabumi earkiyice ka.
\v 12 Kànì mala Ɓakuli ka nda mǝnana ama, sǝm amǝ Yahudi mana sǝm nda ka amǝdǝmba paɓamuru aban Kǝrǝsti ka, ɓǝ̀ sǝm yinǝ ɓwangsǝban andǝ pagulo aban Ɓakuli.
\v 13 Sǝ wun aɓwana mǝnana amǝ Yahudi nda raka, wun gbal ka à yì nyesǝ wun wu pǝlǝna aɓwana mala Ɓakuli, lang wu yi ok cau mǝ'mǝsǝcau nì, yì Cau Amsǝban, sǝ wu paɓamur wun a ban Kǝrǝsti ka. Ɓakuli canba wun nyoulǝa male arǝ wun, mǝnana lǝmdǝ ama angŋǝna wun kǝla amale ka. Sǝ mǝno yì nyoulǝa ka nda Bangŋo Mǝfele a ɓabum wun, mǝnana bangce a pwarian ama nǝ̀ pà ka.\f + \fr 1:13 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Jol 2:28; 2Kor 1:22\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 14 Sǝ yì Bangŋo Mǝfele ka nda lǝmdǝa sǝm aɓa mǝsǝcau ama, agir mǝnana kat Ɓakuli pàcau acea, ama tsǝngŋǝnia nǝ̀ pà sǝmia ka, nda anggo à dumǝna ma'sǝm, bà pwari akmúr aɓwana kat mana à nda ka mala Ɓakuli ka. Pak mǝnia ka ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɓwangsǝi, sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm nggǝ pe wi gulo.\f + \fr 1:14 \ft Ko: \fqa <<Sǝ yì Bangŋo Mǝfele ka Ɓakuli pa sǝmi ɓǝ̀ lǝmdǝ ama mbak-kàngkàng liɓala male ka nda ace sǝm, ba pwari mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ yia e dumǝna ma'sǝm, sǝ anggo ka ɓǝ̀ yinǝi wi ɓwangsǝban andǝ gulo.>>\f*
\s1 Bulǝs pak hiwi ace aɓwana // mala Ɓakuli ɓǝa kum sǝlǝe
\p 
\v 15 Ace mǝnia ka, lang ǝn ongŋǝna ce paɓamuru ma'wun aban Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu andǝ earcearǝu mana wu ndanǝi aban aɓwana mala Ɓakuli a koya ban ngga,
\v 16 ko ǝn usǝlǝki pakki Ɓakuli yàwá ace wun ɗang. Ən nggǝ pak hiwi ace wun pwari-pwari.
\v 17 Ən nggǝ zǝmbi Ɓakuli mǝgulo, yì Tár Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti, ɓǝ̀ pa wun sǝlǝe mala Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli andǝ sǝngir, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu súrǝ̀ Ɓakuli kam kpǝm.
\v 18 Ən nggǝ pak hiwi gbal ama, ɓabum wun ɓǝ̀ lùmsǝ nǝ tǎlaban, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu súrǝ̀ tsǝkɓalǝu mana Ɓakuli tunǝ wun aɓalǝi ka. Sǝ mǝnia yì tsǝkɓalǝu mǝnana nda ace aɓwana male mǝfele ka, nda mǝnana ama, ɓǝa kum agir mǝɓoarne kǝ̀rkǝ́r aɓa liɓala mǝgule, mǝnana Ɓakuli bang ama nǝ̀ pea wia ka.
\v 19 Ɗǝm ngga, ǝn nggǝ pak hiwi ama ɓǝ̀ wu bwalta gulo mala rǝcandǝa mala Ɓakuli mana à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ kane arǝ kǝ ɓe raka, mǝnana ndanǝi ace sǝm, sǝm mǝnana sǝm pa ɓamur sǝm a baní ka. Mǝnia yì rǝcandǝa mana Ɓakuli kǝ pangŋǝ̀nà túró nǝi aɓalǝ sǝm ngga, nda kǝ rǝcandǝa
\v 20 mǝnana loasǝna Kǝrǝsti nǝi a ɓembe nǝ yilǝmu, sǝ dumsǝi a buno-gulo, a bù-mǝlì mala Ɓakuli akanó a kùli ka.\f + \fr 1:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ang 110:1\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 21 A ban mǝno ka, ndanǝ rǝcandǝa kǝ̀rkǝ́r amur koya murǝma, andǝ amǝ'pagara, andǝ amǝ'rǝcandǝa, andǝ amǝ'yálmúrû, andǝ koya buno gulo nani ka; yàle pa amǝnia yì ɓanza nǝmurǝì ɗàng, nda kat andǝ ɓanza mǝno gbal kǝ yiu ka.
\v 22 Ɓakuli nyesǝ koya gìr ka aɓata rǝcandǝa mala Kǝrǝsti, sǝ tsǝk Kǝrǝsti amur girbunda kat, ace ɓoaro mala ikǝlisiya, yia amǝkpate.\f + \fr 1:22 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ang 8:6\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 23 Kǝrǝsti ka nda Múr ikǝlisiya, sǝ ikǝlisiya, yia amǝkpata Kǝrǝsti ka, à nda ka nggūrǝì mǝnana à lùmsǝ nǝ Kǝrǝsti ka, sǝ yì nǝ nggearǝì ka akiban lùmsǝ ko man kat ka, a koya njar.\f + \fr 1:23 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 1:18\xt*\ft .\f*
\c 2
\s1 Bǝsa yilǝmu aɓa Kǝrǝsti
\p 
\v 1 Ɗiɗyal ka, wu nda ka alú ace mgbikiru andǝ acauɓikea ma'wun.\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 2:13\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 2 Amǝno yia apwari ka, wu kǝ dukiado ma'wun aɓa cauɓikea kǝla mǝnana acili amǝ ɓanza kǝ pa, aban kpata Shetan, mana gingginǝ ɓanza mana à sǝngiyi raka, sǝ bangŋo male nda kǝ pak túró aɓalǝ aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ okî Ɓakuli raka.
\v 3 Sǝm kat ka, anggo sǝ sǝm duk ɗiɗyal aɓalǝia aban kpata asuno mala nggūrǝu andǝ aɗenyicau mala ɓamurǝ sǝm, mǝ earce cauɓike. Sǝ mǝnia yì ɓealu ma'sǝm ngga tsǝa sǝm nda aɓata bumlulla mala Ɓakuli kǝla mǝnana ɓwapǝndǝa kat pak ka.
\v 4 Sǝ acemǝnana mǝsǝswatǝr mala Ɓakuli gul kpǝm, sǝ earce sǝm kǝ̀rkǝ́r ka,
\v 5 nda gìr nî sǝ kat andǝ wú mǝnana sǝm wu aɓalǝ acauɓikea ma'sǝm ngga, yi pa sǝm yilǝmu nǝ loasǝo mǝnana loasǝ Kǝrǝsti a ɓembe ka. Kǝ ɓwamuru mala Ɓakuli nda nǝmurǝì amsǝ wun ngga.\f + \fr 2:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Bit 1:3; 2Tim 1:9\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 6 Ɓakuli loasǝ sǝm a lú a tarǝ sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti, sǝ dumsǝ sǝm atè akanó a kùli, acemǝnana sǝm nda aɓa kpapi sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka.
\v 7 Ɓakuli pê anggo ace mǝnana arǝ anza mǝnana à kǝ yiu a dǝmba ka, nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ buì arǝ sǝm. Nǝ̀ na ama, sǝm nda ka túró mala ɓwamuru andǝ mǝsǝswatǝr male mǝgule andǝ mǝɓoarne kǝ̀rkǝ́r, mǝnana lǝmdǝa sǝmi atàcau mala gìr mǝnana Kǝrǝsti Yesu pè ka.
\v 8 Ɓwamuru mala Ɓakuli nda amsǝ wun ngga, nǝ paɓamuru ma'wun a baní. Mǝnia ka, pě ma'wun na ɗang, ɓoro mala Ɓakuli na,\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tit 3:5\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 9 pà ace atúró ɗang, ace mani ka, kǝɓwa ɓǝ̀ kǝa nggori ɗàng.
\v 10 Sǝm nda ka atúróbù mǝgule mala Ɓakuli. Yì ka, pusǝ sǝm abǝshe aɓa kpapi ma'sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti Yesu, ace pakki atúró mǝɓoarne mǝnana ak dǝmba cia ace sǝm ngga.
\s1 Do'mwashat andǝ dorǝpwala // aɓa Kǝrǝsti
\p 
\v 11 Ace mani ka, wun aɓwana mǝnana à ɓǝl wun ngga, wu nda ka amǝ Yahudi raka, wu ɗenyi ama ɗiɗyal ka, wu pa aɓalǝ amǝ Yahudi, aɓwana mana Ɓakuli kùrcau nǝia ka ɗàng. Yia amǝ Yahudi mǝnana à kǝ jali nǝ kasǝ ɓatau ka, à kǝ tunǝ wun ama, <<amǝ ɗwanyi kasǝ ɓatau,>> kat andǝ amani ama kasǝ ɓatau malea ka mala nggūrǝu na, je ɓabumia raka.
\v 12 Aɓa doe ɗiɗyal anggo ka, kǝgìr kpapi wun wunǝ Kǝrǝsti ɗàng. Wu nda ka abǝri mǝnana à pa aɓalǝ amǝ Isǝrayila, aɓwana mǝnana Ɓakuli tària ka ɗàng, sǝ wu pànǝ kāmbe aɓa kùrcau mala Ɓakuli mana kwákítè amur apàcau male a ban aɓwana male ka ɗàng. Wu dukiado ma'wun a ɓanza, wu pànǝ Ɓakuli ɗang, sǝ wu pànǝ tsǝkɓalǝu ɗang.
\v 13 Sǝ a dyan ngga, à dapina wun, wunǝ Kǝrǝsti Yesu. Ɗiɗyal ka, wu tārì Ɓakuli tā wun zak, sǝ adyan ngga, à nyesǝna wun a baní tù nǝ nkila mala Kǝrǝsti.
\p 
\v 14 Kǝrǝsti nǝ nggearǝì ka, yina nǝ dorǝpwala. Aɓa lú male amur nggun-gangndǝi ka, yi dapi amǝ Yahudi andǝ aɓwana mala acili anzali, à duk aɓwana mǝ'mwashati. Yi arki sheran mala ɓinǝ-mǝsǝarǝu mǝnana gau nre sǝm ngga.
\v 15 Nǝ́ lú andǝ lo male a ɓembe ka, yi wal nggurcau andǝ anzongcau, andǝ akúncau mala amǝ Yahudi. Yiu nǝ dorǝpwala a nre ka amǝ Yahudi andǝ aɓwana mǝnana amǝ Yahudi na raka. Yiu nǝ aɓwana mala amǝnia yì akāmbe ɓari ka, ɓǝà duk aɓwana mǝ'mwashati mala bǝsa nzali.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 2:14\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 16 Nǝ́ lú male amur nggun-gangndǝi ka, Kǝrǝsti yinǝ dotarǝu mala amǝ Yahudi andǝ aɓwana mǝnana amǝ Yahudi na raka, aɓa nggūrǝu mwashat andǝa Ɓakuli. Anggo ka, yiu yi kiɗiki ɓibura mǝnana a nre rǝia ka.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 1:20\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 17 Kǝrǝsti yiu yi hamnǝ mǝnia yì cau mǝɓoarne mala dorǝpwala ka a ban wun, wun aɓwana mǝnana amǝ Yahudi na raka, mǝnana wu nda kuko nǝ Ɓakuli ka, andǝ sǝm amǝ Yahudi mǝnana a baní tù ka.\f + \fr 2:17 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 57:19\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 18 Adyan ngga, sǝm kat ka, sǝm nǝ̀ gandǝ yiu a ban Ɓakuli Tárrú aɓa Bangŋo mǝ'mwashati nǝ bu Kǝrǝsti.
\s1 Ɓala Mǝgule ace Mǝtalabangŋo
\p 
\v 19 Sǝ adyan ngga, wun aɓwana mǝnana wu nda ka amǝ Yahudi raka, wu nda ka abǝri andǝ amǝ'kúnɗàngna ɗǝm ɗàng, wu nda ka aɓwana mala nzali mwashat wunǝ aɓwana mala Ɓakuli. Wu nda aɓalǝ amǝɓala mala Ɓakuli.
\v 20 Sǝm dapi kat ka, sǝm dumǝna ɓala male, mǝnana à ɓè amur kusǝɓa mala amǝ'mishan andǝ amǝ'ɓangnǝa mala Ɓakuli ka. Sǝ nggea tali mǝnana kùr kusǝɓǎ ka, nda Kǝrǝsti Yesu nǝ nggearǝì.
\v 21 Kǝrǝsti nda mǝnana tamsǝ mǝnia yì ɓǎ ka kat, bwali arǝarǝia sǝ kǝ tsǝì ɓǝ̀ gulo ɓǝ̀ duk Ɓala Mǝgule ace Mǝtalabangŋo.
\v 22 Nda aɓa kpapi ma'sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti, sǝ wun, aɓwana mǝnana amǝ Yahudi na raka, à nda rǝ ɓak wun gbal wunǝ acili amǝkwaɗi, amǝ Yahudi, ace duk ban-do mala Ɓakuli nǝ bu Bangŋo male.
\c 3
\s1 Túró mishan mala Bulǝs
\p 
\v 1 Ace mǝnia, sǝ mim Bulǝs ka mǝ nda a kùrban ace Kǝrǝsti Yesu, ace wun, wun aɓwana mana wu nda ka amǝ Yahudi raka.
\p 
\v 2 Ɓafo, wu ongŋǝna ama Ɓakuli, aɓa ɓwamuru male ka, panam mǝnia yì túró, mǝ̀ pe ace wun.
\v 3 Kǝla mǝnana ǝn ak dǝmba ǝn gilǝa wun cau amurí mgbeatuk ka, Ɓakuli nǝ nggearǝì, nǝ̀ mǝngiàm ɓá kane male mǝnana nda aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa ka.
\v 4 Ɓǝ̀ wu ɓal gìr mǝnana ǝn gilǝ ka, wun nǝ̀ gandǝ bwalta sǝlǝe mǝnana mǝ ndanǝi aɓa mǝnia yì kane amur Kǝrǝsti ka. Yì kane mǝnana Ɓakuli sǝmbǝrǝ ce ɗiɗyal,
\v 5 sǝ à pusǝì a banfana aban aɓwana arǝ anza mǝno à kutikina ka raka. Sǝa ma adyan a nza man ngga, yi pusǝni a banfana aban amǝ'mishan andǝ amǝ'ɓangnǝa mala Ɓakuli, nǝ bu Bangŋo male.
\v 6 Sǝ mǝnia ka, nda kànì mala Ɓakuli, mana sǝmbǝrǝ ce ɗiɗyal ka. Aɓwana mala acilia anzali andǝ amǝ Yahudi, mǝnana à ak Cau Amsǝban nǝ ɓabumia kat ka, à ndanǝ kāmbe mǝ'mwashati aɓa kum liɓala nǝ atsǝkbu mǝnana Ɓakuli pàcau ace aban amuna male kat ka. Yia kǝm ngga, abare nggūrǝu mǝ'mwashati na, sǝ yia kǝm, aɓa kpapi malea andǝa Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka, Ɓakuli nǝ̀ pea wia agir mǝnana bang ama nǝ̀ pa ka.\f + \fr 3:6 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 1:26,27\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 7 Paɓoro mala Ɓakuli na, atārǝia andǝ ɓwamuru male sǝ à yì pǝlǝam ǝn duk mǝtúró mala mǝnia yì Cau Amsǝban, nǝ rǝcandǝa male mana kǝ pak túró a ɓalǝam ngga.
\v 8 Ko kat andǝ amani ama mǝ nda rítǎu mala aɓwana mala Ɓakuli kat ka, yi pam mǝnia yì ɓwamuru mala banggi aɓwana mǝnana amǝ Yahudi na raka cau male. Yì Cau Amsǝban amur atsǝkbu mǝnana à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ bwal maɗanyia raka, mǝnana à malea na aɓa kpapi malea andǝa Kǝrǝsti ka.
\v 9 Ɓakuli mǝnana pusǝ agir kat sǝ cia aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa a tite ka, tàram ɓǝn bǝlkì koya ɓwa, mǝnia yì gìr sǝmbǝrǝa aɓa kane male ka.
\v 10 Kànì mala Ɓakuli aɓa mǝnia kat ka, nda mǝnana ama, adyan ngga nǝ̀ pak túró nǝ ikǝlisiya, amǝkpata Yesu, nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ sǝlǝe male mǝnana ndakam arǝ anjar ɗàngɗáng ngga, a ban amǝ yálmúrû andǝ amǝ-gara aɓa ɓanza mala abangŋo.
\v 11 Mǝnia ka nda kànì male ɓara-ɓara arǝ anza kat, mǝnana yi lumsǝì aɓa Kǝrǝsti Yesu Mǝtala sǝm ngga.
\v 12 Aɓa kpapi ma'sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti andǝ paɓamuru ma'sǝm a baní ka, sǝm nǝ̀ gandǝ yiu a ɓadǝm Ɓakuli nǝ mǝsǝkang-kangŋa andǝ nzǝmcandǝa.
\v 13 Ace mani ka, ǝn nggǝ zǝmba wun, ɓabum wun ɓǝ̀ kǝa ɓungio ace tanni mǝnana mǝ nda ɓālǝi akani ace wun ngga ɗang, nda àkǝ̀ ce gulo ma'wun.
\s1 Bulǝs pak hiwi ace amǝkpata // Yesu ɓǝa gulo aɓa Bangŋo
\p 
\v 14 Ace mani ka, ǝn ɓun amur ankunam aban hiwi a ɓadǝm Ɓakuli, yì Tárrú
\v 15 mǝnana nǝ baní sǝ amǝɓala male kat, amǝnana a kùli andǝa mǝnana a nzali ka à kum lullǝia ka.\f + \fr 3:15 \fqa mǝnana nǝ baní sǝ amǝɓala male kat, amǝnana a kùli andǝa mǝnana a nzali ka à kum lullǝia ka. \ft Ko <<mǝnana pè koya tàu mala aɓwana mana a kùli andǝ mala aɓwapǝndǝa a ɓanza kat, nggūrǝia mǝnana à súrǝ̀ia nǝi ka,>> Ko <<amur ɓala nggea mǝgule, mala aɓwana mana a kùli andǝa mana a ɓanza ka.>>\f*
\v 16 Ən nggǝ pak hiwi ama, aɓa kume male mǝgule kǝ̀rkǝ́r, mǝnana malkiyi raka, ɓǝ̀ pa wun rǝcandǝa mala ɓabum nǝ bu Bangŋo male.
\v 17 Anggo ka sǝ Kǝrǝsti nǝ̀ do a ɓabum wun, nǝ paɓamuru ma'wun a baní. Sǝ wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ cam kàngkàng aɓa earcearǝu male, kǝla mǝnana nlerǝ nggun kò kpǝm aɓa nzali cam kàngkàng ngga.
\v 18 Ən nggǝ pak hiwi ɗǝm ama, ɓǝ̀ wu kum rǝcandǝa wunǝ acilia ɓwana mala Ɓakuli, wu bwalta tangŋa, andǝ sauwa, andǝ dāh'rya, andǝ lime mala earcearǝu mala Kǝrǝsti.
\v 19 Ən nggǝ zǝmba ama ɓǝ̀ wu súrǝ̀ earcearǝu mala Kǝrǝsti, mǝnana gul kǝ̀rkǝ́r, à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ bwalte kat raka, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu kum lùmsǝo pepe nǝ pa mala Ɓakuli arǝ anjar kat.
\p 
\v 20 Adyan ngga, gulo kat ka, ɓǝà pè Ɓakuli, mǝnana nǝ̀ gandǝ pak gìr mǝnana kútì azǝmba andǝ aɗenyicau ma'sǝm ngga, nǝ rǝcandǝa male mǝnana kǝ pak túró aɓalǝ sǝm ngga.
\v 21 Gulo ka male na aɓa ikǝlisiya, yia amǝkpata Kǝrǝsti Yesu, sǝ aɓa kpapi malea andǝi, aban ká arǝ anza kat, masǝlǝatea pà kàm ɗàng. Ɓǝ̀ do anggo.
\c 4
\s1 Dotarǝu aɓalǝ amǝkpata Kǝrǝsti
\p 
\v 1 Ace mani ka, mim mǝnana mǝ nda a kùrban ace túró mala Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu ka, ǝn nggǝ zǝmba wun ɓǝ̀ ɓeal wun, ɓǝ̀ kārǝa andǝ do mǝnana Ɓakuli earkiyi ce arǝ aɓwana mǝnana tària ɓǝa duk male ka.
\v 2 Ko aya pwari ka, wu nyesǝmur wun, wu duk ɓuɓɓuk nǝ pak munyi nǝ rǝarǝ wun. Wu lǝmdǝià rǝ wun earcearǝu andǝ do nǝ gandǝrǝu.\f + \fr 4:2 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:12,13\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 3 Wu ɓariki, wu dapi múr wun mwashat aɓa Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli, wu kùr rǝarǝ wun a banɓwáná nǝ dorǝpwala.
\v 4 Sǝm kat ka sǝm nda aɓa nggūrǝu mǝ'mwashati, sǝ Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli ka nda mwashat, kǝla mǝnana à pa wun tsǝkɓalǝu mǝ'mwashati mala tunǝban mana Ɓakuli tunǝ wun ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana male ka.
\v 5 Mǝtalabangŋo na mwashat, paɓamuru na mwashat, batisǝma na mwashat,
\v 6 Ɓakuli na mwashat sǝ nda Tár ɓwapǝndǝa kat, nda amur girbunda kat, nda aɓa girbunda kat, sǝ ndanǝ do aɓalǝ sǝm kat.
\p 
\v 7 Sǝ ko yana aɓalǝ sǝm ngga, à pani wi ɓoro mala ɓwamuru mǝnana kārǝa arǝ túró mǝnana Kǝrǝsti pe wi ɓǝ̀ pak ka.
\v 8 Nda gir nî sǝ Malǝmce na ama:
\q1 <<A pwari mǝnana eau nǝi
\q2 aban ká a kùli ka,
\q1 nun ɓwabundǝa mǝnana
\q2 limurǝm amúrià ka atè,
\q1 sǝ pǝlǝa pākî aɓwana aɓoro.>>\f + \fr 4:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ang 68:18\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 9 (Mana nda ɓá mǝnia yì cau ama, <<eau aban ká a kùli>> ka? Ceì lǝmdǝ ama, ɗiɗyal ka Kǝrǝsti sulǝna a tǝta nzali mala ɓanza.
\v 10 Yì ɓwa mǝnana sulǝ a nzali ka, nda kǝ ɓwa mǝnana eau kano ɓong-ɓong amur agirkuli kat ka, ace mǝnana rǝcandǝa male ɓǝ̀ aki ɓanza andǝ kuli ka.)
\v 11 Kǝ yì na mǝnana pākiyi aɓwana aɓoro ka; aɓea ɓwana ka pea wia ɓoro mala túró mishan, aɓea aɓwana ka amǝ'ɓangnǝa mala Ɓakuli, aɓea ɓwana ka amǝham nǝ Cau Amsǝban, aɓea ɓwana ka amǝ'yál aɓwana, sǝ aɓea ɓwana ka amǝkànìgìr.
\v 12 Pāki amǝno yia aɓoro ka, acemǝnana ɓǝ̀ pea aɓwana male rǝcandǝa mala túró ɓak ikǝlisiya, yì nggūrǝ Kǝrǝsti.
\v 13 Mǝnia yì túró ka, nǝ̀ lidǝmba, she ɓǝ̀ sǝm kat, sǝm kya bwalǝna ban-do mǝ'mwashati aɓa paɓamuru andǝ súrǝ̀ Muna mala Ɓakuli ka; she ɓǝ̀ sǝm gulna, sǝm bwalǝna bancame andǝ lùmsǝo mala Kǝrǝsti kǝla mǝnana Ɓakuli earce ka.
\p 
\v 14 Anggo ka, pa sǝm nǝ̀ duk amuna ɗǝm ɗang. Pa sǝm nǝ̀ eare ɓǝ̀ sǝm nggǝ nggaɗiki ɗenyicau ma'sǝm arǝ gir mǝnana sǝm earǝna nǝi ka, nǝ koya bǝsa kanigir mala aɓwana amǝ ɓosǝkiban nǝ anyir aɓa kutan, mǝnana à kùrrì aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa ace swarkiban ngga ɗang.
\v 15 Ma'sǝm ngga, sǝm nǝ̀ nggǝ bang mǝsǝcau aɓa earcearǝu, sǝm nǝ̀ nggǝ gulo a koya njar kat, aban ká pa kǝla Kǝrǝsti Yesu mana nda ɓamur nggūrǝì, yì amǝkpate ka.
\v 16 Yì nggūrǝu ka, Kǝrǝsti na tsǝkiyi ɓǝ̀ duk pepe abanarǝia ka. Koya bare rǝu aɓa pak male yì túró ka, nda rǝ bwalì aɓea abare rǝu ɓǝà gulo, ace mǝnana nggūrǝu kat ka, ɓǝ̀ kǝ gulo nǝ rǝcandǝa sǝ ɓǝ̀ lùmsǝ nǝ earcearǝu.\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 2:19\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 17 Aɓa rǝcandǝa mala Mǝtalabangŋo sǝ ǝn nggǝ na mǝnia yì cau ka: Wu kǝa nyare wu duk ulang do mala amǝ ɗwanyi súrǝ̀ Ɓakuli, mǝnana aɗenyicau malea ka, kǝgìr mǝɓoarne pa aɓalǝi raka ɗang.
\v 18 Ɓabumia ka lùmsǝ nǝ pǝndǝa; à pa aɓa yilǝmu mǝnana Ɓakuli kǝ pa ka ɗang, ace ɗwanyi sǝlǝe andǝ murcandǝa malea.
\v 19 À panǝ kǝsǝkya ɗang. À do ace npel mala nggūrǝia, rǝia kǝ ɓǝla arǝ pak koya gir mɓeami ka.
\p 
\v 20 Sǝ mǝno ka, nda gir mǝnana à kania wun amur Kǝrǝsti ka ɗàng.
\v 21 Ɓafo wun ngga, wu ongŋǝna cau amur Yesu Kǝrǝsti, sǝ wu kanina mǝsǝtacau mǝnana pur nǝ bani ka.
\v 22 Ace mani ka, wu sukki aɓealu mǝ'e ma'wun mala cauɓikea, sǝ wu nying ado mǝ'ɗiɗyali ma'wun, mǝnana à kǝ kánǝ wun nǝ ká aɓa kìɗìkì nǝ swarkiban mala asuno mǝɓane ka.
\v 23 Wu nyinggi Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli njar ɓǝ̀ pa wun bǝsa aɗenyicau andǝ aɓealu.
\v 24 Wu twal bǝsa ɓealu, mǝnana à pusǝì ɓǝ̀ do kǝla Ɓakuli aɓa docauɓoarna, andǝ mǝsǝcau, andǝ do mǝfele ka.\f + \fr 4:24 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:10; Tite 1:26\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 25 Wu ɗeki bu wun arǝ na nyir. Ɓǝ̀ sǝm nea rǝ sǝm mǝsǝcau, acemǝnana sǝm kat ka, sǝm nda mwashat kǝla mǝnana abare nggūrǝu ɓwa pak ka.\f + \fr 4:25 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Zak 8:16\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 26 Ɓǝ̀ bumlulla ma'wun ɓǝ̀ kǝa kánǝ wun a cauɓikea ɗang. Wu kǝa eare ɓǝ̀ pwari lime wu ndanǝ bumlulla più ɗàng.\f + \fr 4:26 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ang 4:4\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 27 Wu kǝa nyinggi Shetan njar ɗàng.
\v 28 Ɓǝ̀ a kǝ́ iun'í ɗiɗyal ka, nying buo arǝì. Pak túró mǝɓoarne nǝ abuo, ace mǝnana wu kúmô wu pe aɓwana mǝnana à ɗwanyi ka.
\p 
\v 29 Wu kǝa eare cau mǝɓane ɓǝ̀ pur a kun wun ɗàng. Wu kǝ nacau mǝnana nǝ̀ ɓakban ngga, ace mǝnana ɓǝa amǝ'oe ɓǝa kum ɓwamuru aɓalǝi.
\v 30 Wu kǝa lul bum Bangŋo Mǝfele mala Ɓakuli ɗang. Wu sǝlǝna ama Bangŋo na kǝ lǝmdǝ ama wu nda ka mala Ɓakuli, sǝ wu nǝ̀ kum àwá a pwari amsǝban ngga.
\v 31 Ace mani ka, wu ɗeki bumkpǝmna, andǝ ukkio mala ɓabum andǝ bumlulla, andǝ kiɗikiɓwa andǝ loasǝkiaban, andǝ acili aɓealu mǝɓike ɗàngɗáng.
\v 32 Wu lǝmdǝià rǝ wun pěmǝɓoarne andǝ ɓuɓɓuka, wu sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr mala rǝarǝ wun, wu twalia rǝ wun banì, kǝla mǝnana Ɓakuli twala wun banì aɓa kpapi ma'wun wunǝa Kǝrǝsti ka.\f + \fr 4:32 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:13\xt*\ft .\f*
\c 5
\s1 Ɓealǝu mǝnana ɓoaro amǝkpata // Yesu ɓǝa dum nǝi ka
\p 
\v 1 Acemǝnana wu nda ka amuna mala Ɓakuli ka, ɓǝ̀ mana wu nǝ̀ pak ka wu kànì arǝ Ɓakuli.
\v 2 Do ma'wun ngga, ɓǝ̀ lùmsǝ nǝ earcearǝu, kǝla mana Kǝrǝsti earce sǝm, sǝ pa yilǝmi duk gir'nkila ace sǝm, mǝnana duk ɓoro mǝɓoarne mana pwasǝbum Ɓakuli ka.\f + \fr 5:2 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 29:18; Ang 40:6\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 3 Nongginǝban, andǝ koya ulang ɓe kǝgìr mǝɓeami, ko nzumon ka, ɓǝa kǝa kumia aɓalǝ wun ɗang. Acemǝnana amǝnia yì agir ka, à kārǝa arǝ do mala aɓwana mala Ɓakuli ɗang.
\v 4 Naki acaubwena, andǝ ndoro mǝɓane, andǝ banggia cau mǝɓange ka, ɓǝ̀ kǝa pur a kun wun ɗang. Kǝ yàwá na wu nǝ̀ nggǝ pakki Ɓakuli ka.
\v 5 Wun nǝ̀ gandǝ sǝlǝe mbak-kàngkàng ama ɓwa mana kat mǝ nongginǝban na, ko mǝ pakki agir'ɓeami na, ko mǝ nzumon na ka, pà nǝ̀ kum kutio a Domurǝm mala Kǝrǝsti andǝ Ɓakuli ɗang. Acemǝnana nzumon ngga, ndá mwashat andǝ peri a ban agirkúncau.
\v 6 Wu kǝa eare aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ ne ɓamuria ama amǝnia yì acauɓikea ka, à kǝgìr na raka, ɓǝa swarki wun ɗang. Acemǝnana bumlulla mala Ɓakuli nǝ̀ sulǝo amur aɓwana mǝnana kat à kǝ kwaɗi cau male raka.
\v 7 Wu kǝa oasǝki abu wun aɓalǝ agir mǝnana amǝnia yì aɓwana pakkiyi ka ɗàng.
\p 
\v 8 Ɗiɗyal ka, wu nda aɓa pǝndǝa, sǝ a dyan ngga, wu kumǝna tǎlaban a bu Mǝtalabangŋo. Acemani ka, wu dukdo mala aɓwana mǝnana à nda aɓa tǎlaban ngga.
\v 9 Acemǝnana mǝnia yì tǎlaban aɓalǝ wun ngga, nda nǝ̀ pusǝ mǝɓoarne, andǝ mana pepè, andǝ mǝnana mǝsǝcau na ka.
\v 10 Wu tsǝk ɗenyicau ma'wun arǝ pak agir mǝnana nǝ̀ pwasǝ bum Mǝtalabangŋo ka.
\v 11 Wu cam zak, wu kǝa oasǝ abu wun aɓalǝ atúró mǝɓane andǝ amǝ ɓealɓike mǝnana aɓwana kǝ pea aɓa pǝndǝa ka ɗàng. A kun mani ka, wu pusǝtea.
\v 12 Nggearǝ gir kǝsǝkya na ɓǝà nacau mala agir mǝnana amǝno yì aɓwana pakkiyi aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa ka.
\v 13 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ tǎlaban yi tana amúrià ka, aɗenyicau malea mǝɓane ka, à nǝ̀ pusǝrǝia a banfana.
\v 14 Acemǝnana tǎlaban ngga kǝ pusǝ koya gir ka a banfana. Nda gìrnî sǝ à na ma,
\q1 <<Loapi ntulo,
\q2 we mǝ'nong-ntulo,
\q1 loapi ɓembe,
\q2 sǝ Kǝrǝsti nǝ̀ po tǎlaban.>>
\s1 Wu gūlì arǝ rǝcandǝa mala // Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli // aɓa do ma'wun
\p 
\v 15 Acemani ka, wu tsǝkir wun arǝ do ma'wun, wu kǝa dukdo mala agǝmɓwa ɗàng, wu dukdo mala amǝkwaro.
\v 16 Wu pak túró nǝ koya dǝmbu mǝnana wu ndanǝi ado ka pepè ace pak gìr mǝɓoarne, acemǝnana apwari mana sǝm nda aɓalǝia ka amǝɓike na.\f + \fr 5:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 4:5\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 17 Wu kǝa pak gìr mǝnana wu pak ɗenyicau amurí raka ɗàng, wu bwalta kusǝ gir mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo earkiyice ama wu pak ka.
\v 18 Wu kǝa wal-walo mùr-anap ɗàng, acemǝnana nǝ̀ kánǝ wun a do kiɗìkì. Wu lùmsǝ nǝ Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli a kúnì.
\v 19 Wu kǝ nea rǝ wun acau mala anggyal ɓwangsǝ Ɓakuli, andǝ anggyal gusǝlǝki Ɓakuli, andǝ anggyal ɓak aɓwana aɓa bangŋo; wu kǝ tu-nggyal ɓwangsǝban andǝ gusǝlǝban nǝ ɓabum wun kat aban Mǝtalabangŋo.
\v 20 Wu kǝ pakki Ɓakuli Tárrú yàwá amur koya gir, a koya bu-pwari ka, aɓa lullǝ Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti.\f + \fr 5:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:16,17\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 21 Ɗǝm ngga, wu kǝ nongsǝ meal wun aɓata rǝ wun, ace kǝ gusǝlǝ Kǝrǝsti.
\s1 Bulǝs kǝ kwarkir amā-ɓala // andǝ aburala
\p 
\v 22 Wun amamǝna, wu nongsǝ meal wun aɓata abura wun, kǝla mǝnana wun nǝ̀ nongsǝî Mǝtalabangŋo ka.\f + \fr 5:22 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:18; 1Bit 3:1\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 23 Acemǝnana ɓwabura ka, nda mur māmí, kǝla mǝnana Kǝrǝsti ka, nda mur ikǝlisiya, yia amǝkpate, sǝ à nda ka nggūrǝì, yì mǝnana nda Mǝ'amsǝia ka.
\v 24 Kǝla mǝnana ikǝlisiya nongsǝ meali aɓata Kǝrǝsti ka, anggo gbal sǝ wun amamǝna ka, wun nǝ̀ nongsǝ meal wun aɓata abura wun aɓa koya gir ka.
\p 
\v 25 Wun aburana ka, wu earce amālá wun, kǝla mǝnana Kǝrǝsti earce ikǝlisiya, yia amǝkpate, sǝ pa yilǝmi kat ace ka.\f + \fr 5:25 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:19; 1Bit 3:7\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 26 Kǝrǝsti pa yilǝmi ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ tàr aɓwana male, yì ikǝlisiya, ɓǝà duk a mala Ɓakuli, nǝ̀ nggǝ lea nǝ mùr lakban mala cau mala Ɓakuli.
\v 27 Pak mǝnia ka, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ yina ace twal ikǝlisiya nǝ̀ pè ɓamúrì ka, ɓǝà kumi gǝraɗau aɓa ɓoarnsari, mǝnana kǝgìr dung, ko kpami, ko kǝgìr mǝpǝndǝke pà kàm arǝì raka; ɓǝ̀ kumi aɓa do tàr ɓamuru ace Ɓakuli andǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ.
\p 
\v 28 Kǝla mǝno ka, dumǝna ama ɓǝ̀ aburana ɓǝà earce amālea, kǝla mǝnana à kǝ earce nggūrǝia ka. Nggearǝ ɓwabura mǝnana earce māmí ka, nda aban lǝmdǝì ɓamúrì earcearǝu.
\v 29 Ɓwa pà nǝ̀ ɓinǝce nggūrǝì ɗàng, she nǝ̀ ɗenyinǝi, nǝ̀ linǝi, kǝla mǝnana Kǝrǝsti kǝ ɗenyinǝ ikǝlisiya, yia amǝkpate ka.
\v 30 Sǝ sǝm ngga, sǝm nda ka abare nggūrǝ Kǝrǝsti.
\p 
\v 31 Kǝla mana Malǝmce ne ka,
\q1 <<Acemani ka, ɓwabura nǝ̀
\q2 ɗeki tárrí andǝ ngge,
\q1 sǝ nǝ̀ lanzǝa arǝ māmí,
\q2 sǝ yia kǝm ngga,
\q1 à dumǝna nggūrǝu
\q2 mwashat.>>\f + \fr 5:31 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 2:24\xt*\ft .\f*
\m 
\v 32 Mǝnia ka, nggea gìr sǝmbǝrǝa mǝgule na, mǝnana à pusǝ ɓālǝi aban aɓwana ɗiɗyal raka, sǝama mǝ ndarǝ bang ama, mǝnia yì cau ka, à nda rǝ kani arǝ Kǝrǝsti andǝ ikǝlisiya.
\v 33 Kat andǝ amani ka, koya ɓwabura ka, dumǝni wi púp ɓǝ̀ earce māmí kǝla mǝnana kǝ earce ɓamúrì ka, sǝ ɓwama gbal ka, dumǝni wi púp ɓǝ̀ pe burí gulo.
\c 6
\s1 Bulǝs kwarkir amuna // andǝ amǝɓǝlia
\p 
\v 1 Wun amuna, wu okî amǝɓǝl wun, acemǝnana wu nda ka mala Ɓakuli ka. Mǝnia ka nda gir mǝɓoarne mǝnana ɓǝa pe ka.\f + \fr 6:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:20\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 2 <<Pe tárró andǝ nggo gulo.>> Mǝnia ka nda nzongcau mǝdǝmbe mǝnana ndanǝ pacau atè ka ama,
\v 3 <<ɓǝa pe tárró andǝ nggo gulo ka, koya gir ka nǝ̀ ginggo a kǝkarì, sǝ yilǝmo nǝ̀ sau a ɓanza.>>\f + \fr 6:3 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 20:12; Nggur 5:16\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 4 Wun atárrú\f + \fr 6:4 \fq Wun atárrú \ft Ko <<Wun atárrú andǝ anggeau>>\f*, wu kǝa wu pakki amuna ma'wun agir mǝnana nǝ̀ cia cau ma'wun nǝ̀ purî bumia ka ɗang, kǝpǝna wu kǝ kwarkiria nǝ kania wia cau mǝnana kǝ puro a kun Mǝtalabangŋo ka.\f + \fr 6:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:21\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Bulǝs kwarkir aguro andǝ // amǝtala-ɓala
\p 
\v 5 Wun aguro, wu okî amǝtala-ɓala ma'wun mǝnana a ɓanza ka, nǝ pagulo nǝ rǝɓǝla. Wu pakkia wia túró nǝ ɓabum wun mwashat, kǝla Kǝrǝsti na wu pakkiyi wi ka.
\v 6 Wu kǝ pwasǝ bumia a koya pwari ka, wu kǝa wu pe acemǝnana mǝsǝia nda arǝ wun ngga ɗàng. Wu kǝ pe acemǝnana wu nda ka aguro mala Kǝrǝsti, wun mǝnana wu kǝ pwasǝ bum Ɓakuli nǝ pakki wi túró nǝ ɓabum wun ngga.
\v 7 Wu pak túró nǝ ɓabum wun mwashat kǝla Mǝtalabangŋo nda wu pakkiyi wi ka, ɓwapǝndǝa nda wu pakkiyi wi ka ɗàng.
\v 8 Wu sǝlǝ ama Mǝtalabangŋo nǝ̀ mbwe ko yana le ka tangnakusǝi, ace túró mǝɓoarne mǝnana pàk ka, ko a nda guro ko a ndanǝ do-ɓamur rǝò.\f + \fr 6:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 3:22-25\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 9 Wun amǝtala-ɓala, wu pakki aguro gbal anggo kǝla mǝnana à banggia wia ama ɓǝà kǝ pang nǝ wun ngga. Wu kǝa pea wia ɓangciu ɗàng. Wu sǝlǝ ama wun kat wunǝia ka, mǝtala-ɓala ma'wun nda a kùli, mǝnana kǝ tàrban raka.\f + \fr 6:9 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 4:1; 3:25; Nggur 10:17\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Wu kùr rǝ wun nǝ agirmunǝo // mala Ɓakuli kat
\p 
\v 10 A masǝlǝate ka, wu tamsǝ kusǝ wun kàngkàng aɓa do kpapi ma'wun wunǝ́ Mǝtalabangŋo andǝ ɓá rǝcandǝa male.
\v 11 Wu kùr rǝ wun nǝ agirmunǝo mǝnana kat Ɓakuli pa wun ngga, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu tamsǝ kusǝ wun kàngkàng arǝ aswárban ɓá kutan mala Shetan.
\v 12 Acemǝnana munǝo ma'sǝm ngga, pa arǝ ɓwapǝndǝa ɗang. Munǝo ma'sǝm ngga, nda arǝ amurǝma ɓá bangŋo mǝɓike andǝ amǝ'yálmúrû mǝɓike mala ɓanza mǝnana à sǝngiyi raka, andǝ arǝcandǝa mala abangŋo ɓá pǝndǝa mǝnana à gingginǝ ɓanza man, andǝ akukwar mǝɓike mǝnana nǝ bumkuli ka.
\v 13 Ace mani ka, wu oasǝ koya girbura mala Ɓakuli, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu cambi ɓi'sǝm mǝbura kàngkàng a pwari mǝɓike. Sǝ anzǝm mana wu pàngŋǝ̀nà koman kat ka, ɓǝ̀ wu tamsǝ kusǝ wun aban came kàngkàng.
\v 14 Ace mani ka, wu cam kàngkàng, wu kpata mǝsǝcau kǝla kùr nggur-ɓunu a taɓunu wun, sǝ wu yál rǝ wun nǝ cauɓoarna kǝla daura-bolo mǝnana amǝ'lwa kǝ oasǝo a kikilia ace mgbàllì amǝsǝ-nta ka.\f + \fr 6:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 11:5; 59:17\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 15 Sǝ do gilǝrǝu ace hamnǝ Cau Mǝɓoarne mala dorǝpwala ka, ɓǝ̀ do kǝla ankura mǝnana wun nǝ̀ oasǝo a kusǝ wun ace túró ka.\f + \fr 6:15 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 52:7\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 16 Tsǝa amur amǝnia yì agir kat ka, wu twal paɓamuru aban Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ do kǝla ntongŋo, mǝnana wun nǝ̀ tamsǝ amundi-bǝsa mala Shetan mǝnana kǝ tura wun ngga.\f + \fr 6:16 \fqa tamsǝna amundi-bǝsa mala Shetan: \ft Ko <<limnggi amundi-bǝsa mala Shetan>>\f*
\v 17 Ɓǝ̀ amsǝban gir múr wun kǝla sukuru-bolo mǝnana wun nǝ̀ oasǝo ace yál ɓamúr wun ngga, sǝ wu pak túró nǝ cau mala Ɓakuli, kǝla nggeabyau mǝnana Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli kǝ pa wun, wun nǝ̀ twal a bu wun ace munǝo ka.\f + \fr 6:17 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 59:17\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 18 Wu pak hiwi aɓa Bangŋo a koya pwari, nǝ koya ulang hiwi andǝ zǝmba amur koya gìr kat. Wu dum nǝ tsǝkiru, wu lidǝmba nǝ hiwi ace amǝ kpata Ɓakuli mǝnana a koya ban ngga.
\p 
\v 19 Wu pak hiwi acem gbal. Wu zǝmbi Ɓakuli, ɓǝ̀ pam cau mǝnana mǝ nǝ na ka, ɓǝ̀ ǝn mǝn kunam mǝ nǝ bǝlki ɓá mǝsǝcau mǝnana Ɓakuli lǝmdǝa sǝmi aɓa Cau Amsǝban ngga.
\v 20 Àkǝ̀ ce mǝnia yì cau ka sǝ mǝ nda a ndàkurban ado, sǝama ǝn lidǝmba nǝ hamnǝ cau, acemǝnana Ɓakuli nǝ́ túrǎm kǝla mǝ'pwantu male. Wu pak hiwi acem ama mǝ camarǝ nakuni nǝ mǝsǝkang-kangŋa, kǝla mǝnana ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ ǝn ne ka.
\s1 Bulǝs masǝlǝta cau male // nǝ makkun
\p 
\v 21 Gir mana mǝ nda ɓālǝi ado, túró mǝnana ǝn pakkiyi ka, andǝ rǝcandǝa mala nggūrǝam ngga, Tikikus nǝ yia bǝla wun ɓālǝi kat. Yì ka, mǝ'eamrǝarǝu na, mǝnana sǝm earkiyi ace raka, sǝ ɓwa na mǝnana dum nǝ mǝsǝcau aɓa túró aban Mǝtalabangŋo ka.
\v 22 Ən tasǝi aban wun àkǝ̀ ce bangga wun cau mala pǎ ma'sǝm, sǝ ɓǝ̀ ɓak ɓabum wun.\f + \fr 6:22 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 20:4; 2Tim 4:12; Kol 4:7,8\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 23 Ɓǝ̀ rǝ wun pwalo, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, sǝ ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli Tárrú andǝ Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu Kǝrǝsti, pà wun ɓabum earcearǝu andǝ domǝsǝcau.
\v 24 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwamuru mala Ɓakuli do atà aɓwana mǝnana kat à earce Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti ka nǝ earcearǝu mǝnana malkiyi raka.
